{"tid":2181201,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"Laliga官方發表聲明,證實梅西的違約金條款依然有效","createTime":"2020-08-30T12:07:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-31T02:00:45.000Z","uid":173952,"like":11,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"e4c03ebbe05bbd07e6c13cc4bd99a78472b1b88d","tid":2181201,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T12:07:25.000Z","msg":"作為西班牙職業聯賽所有球員合同的審查組織,Laliga寫道:<br />\n<br />\n&quot;針對一些過去幾天出現的,在不同媒體上的,關於巴塞羅那球員萊奧內爾-安德雷斯-梅西的合同問題的解讀&mdash;&mdash;很多解讀還是各自完全不同的,Laliga方面希望做出以下澄清:<br />\n<br />\n&quot;目前梅西的合同依然有效,而且合同中依然存在'解約條款',這個條款要求球員如果需要單方面解約需要遵照履行&mdash;&mdash;該條款根據皇家法令1006/1985號第16條,該法令專門用於規範職業運動員的勞工權責。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n&quot;在履行相關的規定的前提下,如果球員不支付合同中規定的解約金額,那麼Laliga也不會對其解約批准生效。&quot;"},{"pid":"2e17bff2d193c2227f7fdcb959c24ee0e9e613e6","tid":2181201,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T12:07:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.laliga.com/noticias/nota-informativa-contrato-lionel-messi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.laliga.com%2Fnoticias%2Fnota-informativa-contrato-lionel-messi&d=lPj0fEAhrWGYZLLoA4iNoAbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=a35cb99e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.laliga.com/noticias/nota-informativa-contrato-lionel-messi</a>"},{"pid":"1bc6c154c00e09e5702ccdab2e1075237c7e59d0","tid":2181201,"uid":68080,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T12:09:42.000Z","msg":"3+1唔好續個1<br />\n應該都係大家反面收場<br />\n美斯就算被逼留都唔會踢架啦"},{"pid":"31f2220bcfabfaa7fe78639adc1f768da921a2b9","tid":2181201,"uid":2611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T12:09:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />打官司未"},{"pid":"bcd4712f2e102d96b66664b2c3075344f49b3289","tid":2181201,"uid":202362,"like":26,"dislike":2,"score":24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T12:09:52.000Z","msg":"西甲已經冇咗尼馬同C朗<br />\n一定盡全力配合巴塞留美斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{